Create a text file with all examples in the video

Create a repository on GitHub and follow steps in this link: https://help.github.com/articles/create-a-repo/
And commit a text file to repository follow below steps:

open terminal 
Step-1: git clone <repository link from GitHub site>
Step-2: git add <your commands file path>
Step-3: git commit -m "comment for your file"
Step-4: git push origin master
